nodes.text: This massage parlor was a business that had locations in slum district G17 and the lower market districts on the planet Coruscant during the Clone Wars. The first was situated next to Lauli Wahlo's noodle shop, Chezdeze, Trueping's, and a Noodle Bar diner. The other massage parlor was located in a marketplace, near the Droid Spa.
The parlor specialized in the treatment of shoulder aches. Luminous Aurebesh signs, like "massage" and "shoulder aches," were put up in order to attract potential customers.
